WEBVTT

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:33.896
GlobalXplorer is an online
crowdsourcing platform

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:37.896
that allows anyone in the world
to help map ancient sites

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.936
by looking at satellite imagery.

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:43.056
And it's this idea
that everyone in the world

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:44.960
can make a contribution to science.

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:46.856
It can be anyone.

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:49.160
(Music)

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:55.896
Doris Jones: I'm Doris Jones,
I'm 90 years old, I live alone

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:58.056
except for my two kitties.

00:01:58.080 --> 00:02:00.216
And I need something to do.